The paper deals with secure content delivery in wireless networks, which involves information theory (IT) and network infrastructure (NI) aspects. The paper also addresses security issues, which fall under the category of cryptography and security (CR). The use of stochastic geometry and optimization techniques suggests that the paper may also belong to the systems and control (SY) or multimedia (MM) categories.
